        Or use `xargs`:
        
        ```sh
        strava activities -q --after="1 day ago" | xargs strava activity 
        ```
        
        Combine JSON output with `jq`:
        
        ```console
        âžœ strava activities -pp 1 -q | xargs strava activity --output json | jq ".name"
        "Afternoon Run"
        ```
        
